#. Tag: title
#: man-kfind.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kfind.1.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Find Files tool is a useful method of searching for specific files on "
"your computer, or for searching for files that match a pattern. An example "
"of this could include searching for files of a particular type or with "
"certain letters in the filename, or that contain a certain piece of text in "
"their contents."
msgstr ""
"Orodje za Iskanje Datotek je uporabna metoda iskanja za specifične datoteke "
"na vašem računalniku ali za iskanje datotek, ki ustrezajo vzorcu, npr. lahko "
"iščemo datoteke določene vrste ali z določenimi znaki v imenu ali tiste, ki "
"imajo določen del besedila v svoji vsebini."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kfind.1.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kfind; is a graphical tool, and not normally run from the command line."
msgstr "&kfind; je grafično orodje in ponavadi ni zagnan iz ukazne vrstice."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kfind.1.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Možnosti"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kfind.1.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "searchpath"
msgstr "pot iskanja"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kfind.1.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may optionally supply a path to prefill the dialog where to start the "
"search."
msgstr ""
"Po želji lahko navedete pot za vnaprejšnje izpolnjevanje pogovornega okna, "
"kjer želite začeti iskanje."

